!nextFragment

00:04.560 --> 00:10.800
principles to design, develop, test, and maintain software systems. It emerged as a distinct discipline
!

00:10.800 --> 00:15.840
in the late 1960s, driven by the increasing complexity of software applications and the need
!nextFragment

00:15.840 --> 00:21.440
for rigorous methodologies to ensure reliability and efficiency. Today, software engineering is
!

00:21.440 --> 00:26.800
integral to virtually every industry, playing a crucial role in developing applications, systems,
!

